descriptionHtml:
Washed Skyrim - Some Food


Where can we get away 
Without eating? 
Without it we go nowhere.


Ver 0.2
Author: Ri4

Description
These mod not only changes the texture, but also the 3D models of objects. The results are visible in the figure.

______________________________

Installation
Use NMM or Move the files to your data directory

Uninstall
Use NMM or Delete the files from your DATE directory
...\\meshes\\clutter\\food\\apple01.nif
...\\meshes\\clutter\\food\\apple02.nif
...\\textures\\clutter\\food\\WS\\ <ALL FILES>
